WEBVTT

01:01.310 --> 01:02.350
Chu.

01:30.950 --> 01:32.400
Chu.

01:33.640 --> 01:34.780
I want to see His Majesty.

01:34.780 --> 01:36.090
I know what you're going to say.

01:36.090 --> 01:37.400
His Majesty is in a bad mood.

01:37.400 --> 01:39.400
You'd better report on another day.

01:39.509 --> 01:41.039
Ever since His Majesty
recovered from his illness,

01:41.039 --> 01:42.920
he's been either searching everywhere
for Queen Chu's whereabouts

01:42.920 --> 01:44.710
or drinking and making merry
in the hunting ground.

01:44.710 --> 01:47.840
Military affairs have already
piled up like a mountain!

02:03.790 --> 02:05.520
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

02:20.800 --> 02:21.560
Speak.

02:22.520 --> 02:24.680
It has been 3 months
since Great Yong withdrew their troops.

02:24.680 --> 02:27.280
Our spies there
brought a secret report today,

02:27.840 --> 02:29.870
saying that Meilin Pass
may seem heavily guarded

02:29.870 --> 02:30.870
and impregnable,

02:31.360 --> 02:33.120
but in reality,
the troops from Xintai Pass

02:33.120 --> 02:34.920
to the east have been moved west.

02:35.710 --> 02:36.870
Now, Xintai Pass

02:37.000 --> 02:39.400
is the most vulnerable place
in Great Yong.

02:39.750 --> 02:41.470
The Yong Army previously

02:41.470 --> 02:42.800
suffered heavy losses
in the Battle of Meilin Pass.

02:42.800 --> 02:45.030
Meanwhile, our Great Yan
has ample rations,

02:45.030 --> 02:48.360
enough to supply an eastward expedition
of 50,000 Yan soldiers.

02:48.360 --> 02:49.120
Your Majesty,

02:49.120 --> 02:51.030
I think we should attack Great Yong

02:51.030 --> 02:52.560
before they have a chance
to catch their breath,

02:52.560 --> 02:54.120
striking at their weakest point

02:54.120 --> 02:55.829
and catching them off guard!

03:07.310 --> 03:08.030
You.

03:09.590 --> 03:10.310
Come here.

03:25.150 --> 03:25.950
Your Majesty.

03:26.360 --> 03:27.150
Look up.

03:32.400 --> 03:34.200
What dance were you performing?

03:34.590 --> 03:36.030
It is Great Yan's war dance.

03:36.030 --> 03:37.829
It praises Great Yan's warriors

03:38.079 --> 03:40.210
for fearing no strong enemy,
expanding territories,

03:40.210 --> 03:41.490
and battling heaven and earth.

03:41.490 --> 03:43.520
Expanding territories.

03:44.870 --> 03:46.680
Battling heaven and earth.

03:47.960 --> 03:48.630
Good!

03:52.079 --> 03:53.340
You shall be rewarded!

04:06.310 --> 04:07.630
Why did you stop me just now?

04:07.630 --> 04:09.000
I rode hundreds of miles overnight

04:09.000 --> 04:10.560
just to get an answer from His Majesty!

04:10.560 --> 04:11.710
Why did you stop me?

04:16.310 --> 04:19.480
Didn't you see His Majesty
was fixated on that dancer,

04:19.829 --> 04:21.920
who looks a bit like Chu Qiao?

04:23.430 --> 04:24.920
What good could possibly come of

04:24.920 --> 04:26.850
discussing military affairs now?

04:28.250 --> 04:28.860
Forget it.

06:04.010 --> 06:09.240
[REBIRTH]

06:09.730 --> 06:12.230
[Episode 10]

06:26.160 --> 06:26.830
Tea.

06:40.430 --> 06:41.230
Your Majesty.

06:51.920 --> 06:53.080
Why are you here?

06:53.560 --> 06:55.560
I am here to serve you, Your Majesty.

06:55.720 --> 06:58.680
Please do not mind my clumsiness.

07:00.800 --> 07:02.310
Which tribe are you from?

07:02.600 --> 07:03.560
Your Majesty,

07:04.600 --> 07:06.000
I am from the Pale Tribe.

07:17.480 --> 07:18.600
Pale Tribe.

07:24.240 --> 07:25.120
Undress me.

07:39.950 --> 07:43.920
The clothes and jewelry
you are wearing are very valuable.

07:44.750 --> 07:46.630
Did Pale's old man reward you

07:47.480 --> 07:49.390
to come and seduce me?

07:51.720 --> 07:53.580
You must be joking, Your Majesty.

07:53.730 --> 07:55.930
Elder Pale is my uncle.

07:56.510 --> 07:57.920
When I was young,

07:58.290 --> 08:01.090
I saw you at my uncle's mansion

08:01.840 --> 08:04.920
and have admired you ever since.

08:12.390 --> 08:13.320
Your Majesty...

08:18.930 --> 08:19.860
Your Majesty...

08:31.160 --> 08:33.039
Tell your self-righteous uncle,

08:33.909 --> 08:35.919
if he tries to play smart next time,

08:36.600 --> 08:37.390
you

08:38.530 --> 08:41.440
won't walk out of here alive so easily.

08:43.240 --> 08:43.870
Get out.

08:55.360 --> 08:56.150
Your Majesty.

08:56.150 --> 08:57.030
Your Majesty, please calm down.

08:57.030 --> 08:58.030
It is my dereliction of duty

08:58.030 --> 08:58.770
to let that dancer...

08:58.770 --> 08:59.730
What dancer?

09:01.000 --> 09:03.320
She is Pale's old man's own niece!

09:04.630 --> 09:06.150
They are so eager

09:06.150 --> 09:07.720
to send their blood relatives

09:07.720 --> 09:09.030
to my side.

09:09.790 --> 09:12.630
What they want to climb onto
is not my bed,

09:13.360 --> 09:14.670
but my throne!

09:16.230 --> 09:17.030
Your Majesty,

09:17.440 --> 09:18.700
forgive my bluntness.

09:19.320 --> 09:20.320
These days,

09:20.600 --> 09:23.480
there has been more restlessness
among the tribes.

09:23.870 --> 09:24.840
Restlessness?

09:30.550 --> 09:32.210
I know without you telling me.

09:33.550 --> 09:34.960
All they're saying

09:34.960 --> 09:37.820
is that the King of Great Yan
has no Queen and no heir.

09:37.960 --> 09:39.550
So it is unknown
who Great Yan will belong to

09:39.550 --> 09:40.840
in the future.

09:41.320 --> 09:42.360
You overthink it, Your Majesty.

09:42.360 --> 09:43.820
The elders wouldn't dare.

09:46.150 --> 09:47.200
Wouldn't dare?

10:24.600 --> 10:25.360
Chu.

10:26.480 --> 10:27.440
In Great Yan,

10:27.910 --> 10:29.510
only the one who can tame this black eagle

10:29.510 --> 10:31.710
is qualified to be the King of Great Yan.

10:31.720 --> 10:32.200
Come.

10:46.690 --> 10:47.290
Chu,

10:47.870 --> 10:49.200
be my Queen of Great Yan.

10:52.870 --> 10:54.330
Who wants to be your Queen?

10:54.600 --> 10:55.550
I don't care.

10:57.390 --> 10:58.450
I didn't lie to you.

10:58.650 --> 10:59.290
Really.

10:59.550 --> 11:00.950
When my father comes to pick me up,

11:00.950 --> 11:02.550
we will go back to Great Yan together.

11:02.550 --> 11:04.430
There are rarely wars

11:04.970 --> 11:06.370
or refugees in Great Yan.

11:06.450 --> 11:07.980
Everyone has enough to eat.

11:08.200 --> 11:08.860
Even slaves

11:09.280 --> 11:10.710
can live as they wish.

11:11.430 --> 11:12.470
Is what you said

11:13.700 --> 11:14.700
true?

11:17.320 --> 11:18.180
It's true, Chu.

11:18.300 --> 11:19.330
When we get there,

11:19.910 --> 11:22.240
no one will ever point a sword
at you again.

11:22.750 --> 11:24.870
I can also take you
hunting horses in Huolei Plains

11:24.870 --> 11:26.740
and soaking in hot springs
in Mount Huihui.

11:26.740 --> 11:28.670
You will definitely like it there.

11:45.120 --> 11:46.870
Please help me bring Chu back.

11:48.910 --> 11:49.910
Bring her back

11:51.390 --> 11:53.250
to make her the Queen of Great Yan.

12:04.270 --> 12:06.300
[Border between Ximeng and Biantang]

12:28.390 --> 12:29.750
One more city ahead

12:29.850 --> 12:31.310
is the border of Biantang.

12:40.910 --> 12:43.250
Once in Biantang,
you must keep a close eye on him.

12:43.250 --> 12:44.800
If there is any sign of trouble,

12:44.800 --> 12:45.940
report immediately.

12:45.940 --> 12:47.420
There can be no mistakes.

12:48.380 --> 12:49.070
Yes.

12:48.890 --> 12:51.070
[Baze, Warrior of the Lingyue Clan]

13:40.750 --> 13:41.440
Fu,

13:41.680 --> 13:42.480
what's wrong?

13:42.570 --> 13:43.830
Are you really scared?

13:44.790 --> 13:46.150
He is not King Ximeng.

13:46.510 --> 13:47.150
What?

14:05.910 --> 14:08.240
I pay my respects

14:08.240 --> 14:09.890
to you with Ximeng etiquette,
Your Majesty.

14:09.890 --> 14:11.690
You are too polite, King Ximeng.

14:11.870 --> 14:13.440
You must be tired from the journey.

14:13.440 --> 14:15.270
We've prepared a state banquet

14:16.440 --> 14:18.550
to welcome you, King Ximeng.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.550
King Ximeng, you coming from afar

14:44.550 --> 14:46.080
to ally with Biantang

14:46.440 --> 14:48.750
is a joy for Biantang.

14:48.960 --> 14:50.820
You are too polite, Your Majesty.

14:50.960 --> 14:52.960
Although Ximeng is in a remote area,

14:53.000 --> 14:55.270
we have long admired the prosperity

14:55.390 --> 14:56.910
and peace of Biantang.

14:57.440 --> 14:59.140
The purpose of my visit this time

14:59.140 --> 15:01.330
is to see the elegance of Biantang.

15:01.870 --> 15:04.870
Thank you for your hospitality.

15:04.870 --> 15:05.750
King Ximeng,

15:06.270 --> 15:07.840
on behalf of Biantang,

15:09.240 --> 15:10.300
I offer you a toast.

15:10.510 --> 15:12.120
To you, Your Majesty.

15:13.200 --> 15:13.870
Wait.

15:14.440 --> 15:16.550
According to the etiquette of Biantang,

15:16.550 --> 15:19.440
wearing a mask at a state banquet

15:20.000 --> 15:21.200
is disrespectful.

15:21.720 --> 15:24.790
King Ximeng, you wear a mask
even when toasting.

15:24.960 --> 15:26.760
Do you have no intention to drink

15:27.750 --> 15:29.240
with His Majesty and me?

15:40.080 --> 15:42.310
It's not that I don't want
to take off the mask,

15:42.310 --> 15:44.460
but my face is strange

15:44.510 --> 15:45.720
and terrifying.

15:45.870 --> 15:47.080
Taking off the mask at a state banquet

15:47.080 --> 15:48.410
would be inappropriate

15:48.440 --> 15:50.630
and impolite.

15:51.150 --> 15:53.480
When you met His Majesty just now,

15:53.670 --> 15:55.550
you used the etiquette of Ximeng.

15:56.020 --> 15:57.330
When toasting,

15:57.670 --> 16:00.200
you are still unwilling
to take off your mask.

16:00.220 --> 16:03.350
Are you so unwilling
to follow the etiquette of Biantang

16:03.600 --> 16:07.400
because you look down on Biantang
as a small Central Plains country,

16:07.600 --> 16:09.630
far less vast than Ximeng,

16:10.030 --> 16:12.080
and thus show no respect

16:12.080 --> 16:13.340
for His Majesty and me?

16:14.150 --> 16:16.480
Why do you make things difficult
for me, Your Majesty?

16:16.480 --> 16:19.200
If you don't want
to take off the mask yourself,

16:19.870 --> 16:21.670
I will ask someone to help you.

16:23.390 --> 16:25.600
You, go and take off his mask.

16:32.430 --> 16:33.550
Useless thing.

16:33.790 --> 16:35.750
How dare you disrespect King Ximeng!

16:35.750 --> 16:36.480
Drag her out!

16:36.870 --> 16:37.630
Beat her to death.

16:37.630 --> 16:39.700
Your Majesty,
please spare my life! Please!

16:39.700 --> 16:41.180
I know my mistake!

16:41.440 --> 16:43.320
Your Majesty, please spare my life!

16:43.320 --> 16:44.530
Your Majesty, please spare my life!

16:44.530 --> 16:46.560
Your Majesty, please spare my life!

16:51.270 --> 16:52.150
You go.

16:55.010 --> 16:57.360
Your Majesty,
please spare my life! Please!

16:57.360 --> 16:58.720
I know my mistake! I know my mistake!

16:58.720 --> 17:01.910
I think those
who have always offended Biantang

17:02.300 --> 17:05.180
and raped and plundered at the border,

17:05.720 --> 17:07.400
although belonging to Ximeng,

17:07.400 --> 17:08.640
must be some

17:08.640 --> 17:11.109
undisciplined savage tribes.

17:11.680 --> 17:13.240
A dignified King Ximeng

17:13.290 --> 17:15.619
can't be such a cruel person.

17:16.349 --> 17:17.720
He will never just watch

17:17.720 --> 17:19.920
innocent people die.

17:28.790 --> 17:29.720
Your Majesty,

17:30.240 --> 17:31.640
I make bold to speak.

17:32.830 --> 17:34.560
King Ximeng is of noble status.

17:34.880 --> 17:36.740
It may be inappropriate for a maid

17:37.000 --> 17:38.130
to take off his mask.

17:38.510 --> 17:40.240
How about letting His Highness

17:40.270 --> 17:42.400
see King Ximeng's true face in person?

17:42.750 --> 17:43.750
What do you think?

17:44.480 --> 17:45.110
Fu,

17:45.440 --> 17:46.430
what are you doing?

17:46.430 --> 17:48.430
I don't quite understand this.

17:49.010 --> 17:51.070
What is your intention, Princess Fu?

17:52.000 --> 17:53.590
King Ximeng came from afar

17:53.650 --> 17:55.110
to make friends with Biantang.

17:55.110 --> 17:56.790
He's probably not refusing

17:56.790 --> 17:58.310
to remove his mask out of disrespect,

17:58.310 --> 18:00.640
but because he
has some unspeakable difficulties.

18:00.640 --> 18:02.960
The Crown Prince is the chosen one

18:03.790 --> 18:04.920
and of noble status.

18:05.200 --> 18:07.400
First, he can replace
the Emperor and the Empress

18:07.400 --> 18:09.130
to see King Ximeng's true face.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.550
Second, if only the Crown Prince goes,

18:11.550 --> 18:12.750
it won't be impolite.

18:12.960 --> 18:16.440
I guess King Ximeng
wouldn't refuse, right?

18:18.480 --> 18:20.590
King Ximeng's face
was disfigured during the war,

18:20.590 --> 18:21.720
so he wears a mask.

18:22.310 --> 18:23.720
By pressing him like this,

18:23.720 --> 18:25.750
are you intentionally
disrespecting our King

18:25.750 --> 18:27.030
to humiliate him?

18:30.200 --> 18:32.310
Since this
is about our diplomatic relations,

18:32.310 --> 18:35.070
let's not let these trivial matters
ruin our harmony.

18:35.070 --> 18:36.790
What do you say, King Ximeng?

18:54.440 --> 18:55.070
Fu.

18:55.070 --> 18:55.720
Ce,

18:56.170 --> 18:57.410
what are you doing?

19:01.070 --> 19:02.510
Mother, Father,

19:02.880 --> 19:03.550
I...

19:04.400 --> 19:05.110
I...

19:07.200 --> 19:09.480
I was afraid King Ximeng's terrifying face

19:09.480 --> 19:11.680
would ruin everyone's good mood today,

19:11.680 --> 19:13.810
so I wanted to share the burden for you.

19:14.240 --> 19:15.700
Ce, since that's the case,

19:16.000 --> 19:18.110
you can take a look
at King Ximeng's true face

19:18.110 --> 19:20.200
on behalf of His Majesty and me.

19:47.770 --> 19:48.730
Ghost!

19:58.960 --> 20:01.620
Apologies for frightening you,
Your Highness.

20:03.310 --> 20:04.350
Ghost!

20:07.310 --> 20:07.960
Ce,

20:08.350 --> 20:09.750
what exactly did you see?

20:11.030 --> 20:12.640
Mother, Father,

20:13.440 --> 20:15.550
I have seen King Ximeng's true face.

20:15.750 --> 20:17.230
It is indeed as King Ximeng said.

20:17.230 --> 20:19.790
His old wounds haven't healed,
so he shouldn't show his face.

20:19.790 --> 20:21.440
So it is true.

20:21.460 --> 20:23.510
His face is exceptionally
ugly and disfigured.

20:23.510 --> 20:24.910
Absolutely terrifying.

20:25.310 --> 20:25.960
Mother,

20:26.350 --> 20:28.480
it's best not to let him
take off his mask.

20:28.480 --> 20:29.350
Alright,

20:29.550 --> 20:31.950
he has seen his face.
Let the banquet begin.

20:32.240 --> 20:33.640
Your Majesty, please wait.

20:33.640 --> 20:36.720
We have specially arranged
a performance for King Ximeng,

20:36.720 --> 20:38.180
and it hasn't started yet.

20:43.550 --> 20:45.480
These 3 Ximeng warriors

20:46.030 --> 20:47.760
are all exceptionally strong,

20:47.850 --> 20:51.850
yet they raped and pillaged
on our Biantang land.

20:51.920 --> 20:53.030
I thought,

20:53.030 --> 20:56.160
why not take the opportunity
of King Ximeng's visit today

20:56.160 --> 20:59.550
to let our Biantang warriors
and Ximeng warriors

21:00.240 --> 21:01.840
compete against each other?

21:08.860 --> 21:09.990
Let the match begin.

21:12.800 --> 21:14.720
You can't even hold your swords steadily.

21:14.720 --> 21:16.200
If Ximeng people are like this,

21:16.200 --> 21:18.460
how dare they call themselves warriors?

21:18.960 --> 21:19.960
In my opinion,

21:20.260 --> 21:22.720
they're nothing but cowards, not warriors!

21:36.750 --> 21:38.240
I thought

21:38.240 --> 21:41.170
Ximeng soldiers were so brave
and skilled in battle.

21:42.000 --> 21:43.850
I didn't expect to see today

21:44.240 --> 21:45.700
that they are so pathetic.

21:45.920 --> 21:47.750
They are just like beasts.

21:49.160 --> 21:51.310
These 3 warriors are obviously weak.

21:51.310 --> 21:52.830
They look like
they haven't eaten for days.

21:52.830 --> 21:54.680
This is simply bullying the weak!

21:54.680 --> 21:55.470
Continue.

22:11.240 --> 22:13.300
Your Majesty, please take our bodies

22:13.830 --> 22:15.110
back to Ximeng.

22:47.110 --> 22:47.890
My Queen,

22:47.910 --> 22:49.910
King Ximeng came from afar.

22:50.160 --> 22:52.880
Randomly picking some soldiers
to start a fight

22:52.900 --> 22:55.180
is against our way of treating guests.

22:57.310 --> 22:59.570
Your Majesty, you're absolutely right.

23:01.270 --> 23:03.470
The Queen of Lingyue has a noble status.

23:03.590 --> 23:04.440
If it's a match,

23:04.440 --> 23:06.550
she shouldn't compete with soldiers.

23:06.550 --> 23:07.920
Why not...

23:10.000 --> 23:11.350
let Princess Fu do it?

23:11.830 --> 23:14.390
Princess Fu is the daughter
of the Prince of Pingnan.

23:14.390 --> 23:16.510
Not only is she a noble lady
of the mansion,

23:16.510 --> 23:18.840
but she also
came from a family of generals.

23:18.840 --> 23:21.400
She was raised and taught
by the Prince of Pingnan from childhood.

23:21.400 --> 23:23.200
To compete against the Queen of Lingyue

23:23.200 --> 23:24.680
is perfectly suitable.

23:26.030 --> 23:26.590
Mother,

23:26.880 --> 23:27.960
Fu is still injured.

23:27.960 --> 23:29.490
-Don't worry.
-I'm afraid—

23:29.610 --> 23:32.200
Princess Fu, like the Queen of Lingyue,

23:32.790 --> 23:34.160
is of noble status.

23:34.720 --> 23:38.160
The so-called match
is just a friendly spar.

23:38.680 --> 23:41.010
They should stop before anyone gets hurt.

24:02.400 --> 24:04.000
Don't you know martial arts?

24:04.200 --> 24:05.180
Why didn't you fight back?

24:05.180 --> 24:06.980
I came from a family of generals.

24:07.030 --> 24:08.830
We only lead troops into battle,

24:09.200 --> 24:10.930
not engage in reckless brawls.

25:11.170 --> 25:11.810
Enough.

25:15.130 --> 25:17.030
The Queen of Lingyue lacks manners

25:17.030 --> 25:18.560
and injured your princess.

25:18.670 --> 25:19.950
Please forgive us.

25:20.110 --> 25:20.750
It's fine.

25:21.370 --> 25:22.570
In a match,

25:23.000 --> 25:24.530
accidents are inevitable.

25:32.960 --> 25:35.480
We startled King Ximeng today.

25:35.920 --> 25:37.920
It is truly Biantang's negligence.

25:38.070 --> 25:40.550
I hope such a trivial matter

25:41.030 --> 25:44.000
won't affect the friendship
between Ximeng and Biantang.

25:44.000 --> 25:45.550
I came from thousands of miles away

25:45.550 --> 25:47.880
to build good relations with Biantang.

25:47.920 --> 25:49.110
Swords have no eyes.

25:49.130 --> 25:52.260
Those plundering Ximeng warriors'
deaths are trivial,

25:52.550 --> 25:55.960
but harming our diplomatic relations
would not be worth it.

25:55.960 --> 25:58.160
King Ximeng, you're absolutely right.

25:58.240 --> 26:00.350
You must be like me,

26:00.480 --> 26:02.110
hoping for good relations
between our countries,

26:02.110 --> 26:04.480
which is why you helped Princess Fu.

26:05.270 --> 26:06.920
However, I feel that

26:07.110 --> 26:09.790
Princess Fu and King Ximeng

26:10.070 --> 26:11.960
have quite a deep connection.

26:12.500 --> 26:14.900
King Ximeng
was unwilling to show his face,

26:14.960 --> 26:18.420
yet the Crown Prince and Princess Fu
stepped in to help him out.

26:18.750 --> 26:21.640
When Princess Fu
dueled with the Queen of Lingyue,

26:22.310 --> 26:25.000
King Ximeng also lent a hand.

26:25.000 --> 26:26.480
Why do I feel

26:26.750 --> 26:31.070
that King Ximeng, the Crown Prince,
and Princess Fu

26:31.480 --> 26:33.010
share some past connection

26:33.280 --> 26:36.040
that we don't know about?

26:36.480 --> 26:39.440
How could the Crown Prince
have a connection with King Ximeng?

26:39.440 --> 26:41.160
Ximeng is a remote region,

26:41.160 --> 26:43.760
and it's King Ximeng's first time
in Biantang.

26:44.000 --> 26:44.640
This...

26:44.660 --> 26:47.100
Is Her Majesty implying something?

26:48.070 --> 26:49.930
Your Majesty, you must be joking.

26:49.960 --> 26:51.590
King Ximeng is highly skilled

26:51.590 --> 26:52.640
and very proud.

26:53.270 --> 26:55.120
He won't even reveal his true face;

26:55.120 --> 26:56.520
he is no ordinary person.

26:57.000 --> 26:57.960
How could I

26:57.960 --> 27:00.100
possibly establish a connection
with him so easily?

27:00.100 --> 27:03.230
Naturally, I would like to befriend
King Ximeng as well.

27:03.270 --> 27:05.330
But I'm afraid in King Ximeng's eyes,

27:05.400 --> 27:07.720
no one is worthy of his trust.

27:13.110 --> 27:14.720
Princess Fu, you're joking.

27:15.160 --> 27:18.750
I felt like old friends with His Highness
and Princess Fu at first sight.

27:18.750 --> 27:20.720
I have no intention of being arrogant.

27:20.720 --> 27:21.480
Alright.

27:22.000 --> 27:23.600
This has gone on long enough.

27:23.750 --> 27:24.960
I am tired.

27:24.960 --> 27:27.720
Since the Crown Prince
and King Ximeng feel like old friends,

27:27.720 --> 27:30.400
then the Crown Prince will be in charge

27:30.830 --> 27:32.220
of King Ximeng's itinerary in Biantang.

27:32.220 --> 27:33.020
Crown Prince,

27:33.200 --> 27:37.330
if you are unsure about anything,
ask Lord Wang from the Ministry of Rites.

27:57.530 --> 28:00.050
How could Zhuge Yue become King Ximeng?

28:02.000 --> 28:02.550
Qiao,

28:02.920 --> 28:03.980
don't stay silent.

28:04.160 --> 28:04.880
Are you hurt?

28:04.880 --> 28:07.480
-I'll send the imperial physician to you.
-I'm fine.

28:07.480 --> 28:09.310
I know you saw Zhuge Yue today,

28:09.310 --> 28:10.440
and you are in a bad mood,

28:10.440 --> 28:11.030
but it's okay.

28:11.030 --> 28:12.090
Stop the carriage.

28:14.160 --> 28:14.960
What's wrong?

28:15.270 --> 28:16.330
I have things to do.

28:16.720 --> 28:17.720
You go back first.

30:24.850 --> 30:27.760
♪ We mock karma ♪

30:28.510 --> 30:31.090
♪ For being unfair ♪

30:31.500 --> 30:33.480
♪ Why is life ♪

30:33.690 --> 30:37.750
♪ Often filled with regrets? ♪

30:39.200 --> 30:39.940
Xing.

30:39.440 --> 30:42.260
♪ My body scarred and worn ♪

30:41.510 --> 30:42.590
Zhuge Yue.

30:42.630 --> 30:45.850
♪ My soul lain bare and torn ♪

30:45.880 --> 30:47.510
Ahead is the border of Great Yan.

30:46.500 --> 30:48.020
♪ I pass along ♪

30:48.160 --> 30:49.510
Let's part ways here.

30:48.300 --> 30:52.240
♪ This fleeting world's chaotic song ♪

30:53.310 --> 30:54.000
Xing.

30:53.870 --> 30:57.250
♪ My heart holds quiet words ♪

30:55.000 --> 30:57.160
Yan Xun is no longer who he used to be.

30:57.400 --> 31:00.500
♪ Words I cannot speak at all ♪

30:57.680 --> 30:59.080
Why do you still help him?

30:59.480 --> 31:01.480
Yan Xun didn't choose to become like this.

31:00.940 --> 31:02.620
♪ Hate and woe ♪

31:02.400 --> 31:05.200
Who is the real culprit?

31:03.000 --> 31:07.000
♪ All is out of my control ♪

31:06.480 --> 31:07.960
This is the path I chose.

31:08.440 --> 31:10.880
♪ The snow falls ♪

31:08.550 --> 31:09.550
I won't look back.

31:10.270 --> 31:11.310
I will go back to help him.

31:11.290 --> 31:14.460
♪ With fate ♪

31:11.880 --> 31:13.160
Wherever there are people in this world,

31:13.160 --> 31:14.820
there will be power struggles

31:15.070 --> 31:16.310
and people preying on each other.

31:15.300 --> 31:16.540
♪ It will eventually ♪

31:16.790 --> 31:18.070
The perfect world you want

31:16.990 --> 31:18.990
♪ Fall before ♪

31:18.640 --> 31:19.880
simply doesn't exist.

31:19.010 --> 31:21.470
♪ The dawn ♪

31:20.240 --> 31:20.960
Zhuge Yue,

31:21.950 --> 31:24.160
♪ As a foreigner ♪

31:22.110 --> 31:24.310
this is the difference between you and me.

31:24.310 --> 31:26.110
You accept the rules of this world,

31:24.330 --> 31:28.880
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

31:26.350 --> 31:27.310
but I don't.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.880
Since you chose this path yourself,

31:29.170 --> 31:31.440
♪ Wander ♪

31:30.510 --> 31:31.830
even if it leads through
a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood,

31:31.660 --> 31:35.870
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

31:31.830 --> 31:33.110
you will walk it alone.

31:34.830 --> 31:35.590
But if one day,

31:35.590 --> 31:37.590
you find you can no longer
take a step forward,

31:36.350 --> 31:38.590
♪ The lock in my heart ♪

31:38.200 --> 31:39.310
you know the way

31:38.790 --> 31:40.220
♪ Put the memories ♪

31:40.250 --> 31:44.120
♪ In the silence of the night ♪

31:40.920 --> 31:42.250
back to Qingshan Manor.

31:44.850 --> 31:45.850
♪ Wait ♪

31:46.410 --> 31:50.940
♪ For the stars and moon
to part ways again ♪

31:51.070 --> 31:53.280
♪ As a foreigner ♪

31:51.830 --> 31:53.350
If you turn around one day,

31:53.450 --> 31:58.000
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

31:54.070 --> 31:54.750
I'll be

31:55.400 --> 31:56.640
right behind you.

31:58.280 --> 32:00.560
♪ Wander ♪

32:00.780 --> 32:04.990
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

32:05.640 --> 32:07.740
♪ Traveling alone ♪

32:08.040 --> 32:10.040
♪ In a world ♪

32:10.060 --> 32:13.620
♪ Where fate is unkind ♪

32:13.650 --> 32:14.820
♪ Look ♪

32:15.220 --> 32:19.430
♪ The mortal world has forgotten me ♪

32:20.970 --> 32:22.520
♪ I wish ♪

32:22.990 --> 32:31.350
♪ You'll forget me ♪

32:38.400 --> 32:40.240
Oh no! The stable is on fire!

32:40.750 --> 32:42.310
Hurry, put out the fire! Hurry!

32:42.310 --> 32:43.070
Put it out!

32:43.240 --> 32:44.170
Put out the fire!

32:44.590 --> 32:46.510
Hurry! Get water!

32:48.030 --> 32:48.920
Go fetch water!

32:48.920 --> 32:49.850
What's going on?

32:51.110 --> 32:51.830
Your Majesty,

32:51.830 --> 32:52.510
it's nothing serious.

32:52.510 --> 32:53.590
Just the haystacks in the stable

32:53.590 --> 32:54.590
caught fire somehow.

32:54.590 --> 32:56.160
I've ordered men to search the vicinity

32:56.160 --> 32:57.720
to see if there's anything unusual.

32:57.720 --> 32:58.440
No need.

32:59.110 --> 33:01.680
The weather is dry,
making it easy for things to catch fire.

33:01.680 --> 33:03.070
Everyone is tired today.

33:03.070 --> 33:04.470
Let everyone rest early.

33:05.000 --> 33:05.480
Yes.

33:36.070 --> 33:37.270
The person who came today,

33:37.270 --> 33:38.930
Princess Fu from the banquet,

33:39.000 --> 33:40.200
is the woman you wanted
to use the Bone-Chilling Grass

33:40.200 --> 33:41.110
to save.

33:46.310 --> 33:47.240
I'm warning you.

33:48.240 --> 33:50.750
Since you saved her,
don't cause any more trouble.

33:50.750 --> 33:52.090
Although I can't kill you,

33:52.090 --> 33:53.460
I can kill her.

33:58.440 --> 33:59.440
Give it back to me!

34:00.780 --> 34:01.950
This wood carving

34:02.160 --> 34:04.490
is the token
of the Lingyue Clan, isn't it?

34:05.270 --> 34:06.160
Five years ago,

34:06.200 --> 34:08.520
King Ximeng led troops
to annex the Lingyue Tribe.

34:08.520 --> 34:10.070
King Lingyue fought to the death

34:10.070 --> 34:11.670
and was tortured to death by King Ximeng.

34:11.670 --> 34:13.670
And the Queen of Lingyue
betrayed her own country

34:13.670 --> 34:14.929
to follow King Ximeng.

34:15.110 --> 34:17.070
She was cursed by her own people.

34:18.960 --> 34:19.880
The Queen

34:20.920 --> 34:21.920
is you, right?

34:21.940 --> 34:23.380
Who told you?

34:23.510 --> 34:24.880
A highly skilled

34:24.880 --> 34:26.550
and arrogant woman

34:27.230 --> 34:30.000
is actually willing
to be King Ximeng's slave.

34:41.760 --> 34:43.230
Since I made a promise,

34:43.230 --> 34:44.889
I will definitely fulfill it.

34:45.280 --> 34:47.710
But if you dare to threaten me
with Chu Qiao again,

34:47.710 --> 34:49.840
none of us will leave Tangjing alive.

34:50.400 --> 34:52.060
I don't care about my own life.

34:52.980 --> 34:55.179
And I care even less about your mission.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.430
Wait.

35:43.230 --> 35:45.230
[Tangjing, Biantang]

35:50.280 --> 35:52.110
Little rabbits! Come take a look!

35:52.110 --> 35:53.370
They're home-raised.

35:53.440 --> 35:54.370
Little rabbits!

35:58.030 --> 35:58.880
Yan Xun.

36:11.150 --> 36:11.840
Chun'er.

36:12.840 --> 36:13.440
Chun'er?

36:14.960 --> 36:15.760
What's wrong?

36:17.920 --> 36:18.480
Nothing.

36:26.070 --> 36:26.710
Chun'er.

36:28.880 --> 36:29.440
Chun'er.

36:30.590 --> 36:31.110
Guess

36:31.550 --> 36:33.080
what I brought back for you.

36:34.070 --> 36:34.960
Today on the street,

36:34.960 --> 36:36.320
I saw you staring at it,

36:37.000 --> 36:38.660
so I guessed you might like it.

36:39.000 --> 36:40.510
My mansion has always been quiet.

36:40.510 --> 36:42.760
I figured you'd get bored
staying here all day.

36:42.760 --> 36:44.760
So I went back to the archery stall

36:44.840 --> 36:45.840
and won it for you,

36:46.110 --> 36:47.970
hoping it could keep you company.

36:54.120 --> 36:54.770
Chun'er!

36:55.670 --> 36:57.270
Chun'er, what are you doing?

36:57.360 --> 36:58.550
You said it yourself

36:58.670 --> 37:00.030
this was a gift for me.

37:00.030 --> 37:02.030
How I deal with it is my own business!

37:07.320 --> 37:07.980
The rabbit!

37:09.500 --> 37:10.770
It's yours, indeed.

37:11.360 --> 37:13.220
But what did that rabbit do wrong?

37:13.500 --> 37:14.880
Why were you so cruel to it?

37:14.880 --> 37:15.360
Yes!

37:15.810 --> 37:17.560
I am cruel and vicious.

37:17.590 --> 37:19.070
Nobody likes me at all.

37:19.150 --> 37:20.670
Everyone hates me!

37:20.670 --> 37:22.530
So why do you still bother with me?

37:22.840 --> 37:23.630
Just go!

37:23.870 --> 37:25.230
Go away!

37:25.710 --> 37:27.360
All you men are liars anyway.

37:27.530 --> 37:30.530
Sooner or later,
you'll lie to me and bully me!

37:41.670 --> 37:42.400
Chun'er.

37:43.280 --> 37:44.000
I'm sorry.

37:45.670 --> 37:48.070
You must have suffered
a lot of grievances.

37:48.280 --> 37:49.230
But here with me,

37:50.550 --> 37:52.950
I definitely won't let you suffer anymore.

38:01.150 --> 38:01.840
Chun'er.

38:03.360 --> 38:06.030
I will protect you
for the rest of my life.

38:29.520 --> 38:30.930
You can't even kill me.

38:31.140 --> 38:32.340
How can you kill them?

38:32.960 --> 38:34.770
Your Majesty, please don't be sad.

38:34.770 --> 38:36.250
Just punish me.

38:36.440 --> 38:38.510
Based on my understanding of Zhuge Yue,

38:38.510 --> 38:41.000
his visit to Biantang this time
is not simple.

38:41.000 --> 38:41.780
Chu,

38:42.400 --> 38:43.470
I miss you so much.

38:43.510 --> 38:45.470
I pay my respects to you,
Princess Consort Helian.
